(9, '73DAT07', 0, 73, 5, 'SHELL2 Bed 2 Bath 2nd floor Condo (xxxx) in Lely Resort, Naples, SW Exposure, Sleeps up to 4 persons', 'CFXXX', '2013-05-01', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', 'Cassie', 'Island Escapes', '', '', '', '', 'This condo features a large screened lanai with views of the pool/spa area and a South Westerly aspect. Amenities include the Coral Falls tropical waterfall pool and spa, two magnificent 18-hole championship golf courses, walking and biking trails, and an abundance of fishing lakes.', 'Coral Falls is a small condominium community located on 4.5 acres near the junction of Collier Boulevard and US-41 in Naples, Southwest Florida - part of the Lely Resort complex.\r\n\r\nAmenities at Lely Resort offer a casual resort environment, from a morning tee time to an afternoon tennis game and a leisurely dip in one of the many pools. Residents at Lely fill their days with a variety of activities including fitness classes, card games, shopping trips and so much more. Some of the Lely Resort facilities may require extra payment to use as a guest.\r\n\r\nAt Lely Resort you will be living within steps of not one or two, but three championship golf courses designed by some of the best players in the game’s history. At Lely Resort there are 54 holes of Florida’s greatest golf, with fairways and greens that offer infinite challenge.\r\n\r\nThere is also a large grassed picnic area with Tiki huts and BBQs for guests to use behind which is a large natural woodland.\r\n\r\nAs a renter at Coral Falls Resort you may enjoy the Lely Resort and discover all of the natural beauty that the community has to offer. From the 30 miles of sidewalks, you can walk past homes that are priced up to well over $2 million. You can enjoy sweeping views of the three beautiful golf courses or pause to enjoy the birds on the many fine lakes. There is always an element of suspense during these walks when you pass by the “Alligator Warning” signs. With the everglades almost across the street – who knows if this is the day that an alligator will wander into Lely Resort to also enjoy the amenities? \r\n\r\nIt’s not just a community, it’s a lifestyle!\r\n\r\nIf you decide to go to downtown Naples, simply drive US-41 west for about 8.5 miles which will take about 20 minutes or more depending on traffic. The Naples beaches are only a little further and can be accesses from most east/west streets. To go to Marco Island, simply take Collier Blvd. south for about 15 minutes and when you cross the Judge SS Jolley Bridge you are there.', 218, 5, 8, 8, 6, 'fl34113', 'Naples, FL 34113, USA', 'Lely Resort, Naples', '26.0533532', '-81.745884', 'Naples', 'Fort Myers', 10.00, 40.00, '2', NULL, 2, 2.0, 1, '4', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 4, '0', 'USD', '', NULL, '1', '1', '1', '1', '1', '1', '0', '1', '0', '0', NULL, '', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, 0),
