(39, '73DAT36', 0, 73, 5, 'Relax and unwind in a 1 Bed Suite at Olde Marco Island Inn and Suites. FREE NIGHT SPECIAL OFFERS!', 'Book via Travalco', '2013-11-08', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', '', 'Travalco', '', '', '', '', 'The Olde Marco Island Inn & Suites is located in the heart of Macro Island, close to Naples Museum of Art, Carribean Gardens, Alan Brown Gallery and Botanical Gardens.  Free self-parking. Two double beds in the bedroom and a sleeper sofa in the living area. Bonus Features:\r\nInternet access.', 'The Olde Marco Island Inn and Suites is located in the heart of Macro Island, close to Naples Museum of Art, Caribbean Gardens, Alan Brown Gallery and Botanical Gardens.  Amenities include a restaurant, cocktail lounge, live entertainment (seasonal), business center and safe deposit at the front desk. Recreational facilities include a swimming pool.\r\n\r\nThe Patio gardens of the Olde Marco Island Inn and Suites reflect the tropical heritage in the exclusive usage of native plants. The gardens have been honored with awards for their sensitive use of local flora and fauna.\r\n\r\nYou can sunbathe the day away beside the tranquil heated pool and new hot tub surrounded by the lush greenery of the gardens and the historic beauty of the Inn. Chaise lounges and large terry towels are readily available.\r\n\r\nFree self-parking. Housekeeping: Maid service for general cleaning is available at $35 per service. Towel replacement and trash removal service is available at $15 per service. Both services must be scheduled 24 hours in advance.\r\n\r\nThe historic Inn houses one of Marco Island\\\\\\''s premier award winning restaurants which has been recognized by Gourmet Magazine, named one of the ten best restaurants by Gulf Shore magazine, is a multiple platinum plate award winner and was named one of the 100 finest places to dine in the State of Florida by Trend Magazine.  Dinner is served daily from 5:00 p.m. to 10:00 p.m.\r\n\r\nThe Olde Marco Inn is located minutes from some of the most beautiful, well kept beaches in Southwest Florida, which can be accessed by the public at two different locations, Tigertail and South Marco Beach.\r\n \r\nMarco Island - the largest of the Ten Thousand Islands - features a magnificent shoreline that stretches from Tigertail to South Beach. Enjoy miles of clean, uncrowded beaches of white sand and famous Marco sunsets.', 218, 5, 9, 10, 0, 'FL34113', 'Marco Island, FL 34145, USA', '', '25.8728864', '-81.669253', 'Fort Myers', 'Miami International', 45.00, 100.00, '3', NULL, 1, 1.0, 1, '4', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 4, '1', 'USD', '', 'From the 2nd September 2014 every 7th night is free through to the 31st March 2015. Please request rates after the 22nd December 2014.', '1', '1', '1', '1', '1', '1', '0', '1', '1', '0', NULL, '', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, 0),
