(81, 0, NULL, '0', 1, 'Deal A Trip', 'UK', 'no_owner_pic.jpg', '2013-04-01', '2013-04-03', '9', 'Guest comments about Pelican Cove, Bradenton Beach, Anna Maria Island, Florida', '“right across the street from a beautiful beach - the best of both worlds - a beautiful sunrise on one side and a beautiful sunset on the other!” “there is a stop nearby for the free trolley/bus” “We caught some great free music evenings on nearby Bridge Street, and the market on Sundays”', '“The bicycling/walking path along the Coquina Beach Park & the Bay is beautiful!” “many restaurants within walking distance and nearby” “for shoppers, there\\''s an outlet mall nearby” “so many lovely places to ride, and a bike trail right across the street” “The views of the sunrise and sunset were amazing” “prefer the condos that face the bay as the water view is much better” “view over the gulf (from the condos) can be obscured by the trees that run along the beach” “we were able to walk to shops and a great ice cream place” “I recommend Pelican Cove highly and look forward to our stay each year!” “The family enjoys the beautiful crystal clear beach, the pool and jacuzzi. Fishing is great! And the condos are well maintained!” “The location is perfect looking out over the bay and no street noise. The views were beautiful. Everyone was happy all the time. The beach was beautiful. It was a perfect vacation”', '1'),
(82, 0, NULL, '0', 1, 'Deal A Trip', 'UK', 'no_owner_pic.jpg', '2013-04-01', '2013-04-03', '9', 'More Guest Comments about Pelican Cove, Anna Maria Island', '“Great to be able to walk to restaurants, shops & along the piers”', '“Our family come to the beautiful, warm weather on Anna Maria Island. We caught lots of fish and enjoyed many days by the pool and beach. The view of the ocean from the porch was beautiful and we got to watch many amazing sunsets. We even had the opportunity to see dolphins as we were on the beach, very cool! We wish we could stay here forever! Thanks!” “We loved the location of Unit 5 in Pelican Cove. It has the best views of the Gulf and Inter-coastal water ways. You can see the beautiful sunrise from the bedroom balcony and the breath taking sunset from the living room balcony. I love the layout of this condo” “I would remind readers that there is no elevator, so be prepared to walk up with your bags and groceries”', '1'),
